name: Rick
line: The election’s got these yellow shirts more riled up than a Picture Day Jessica.

name: Rick
line: You make fun of me all the time, and now you got me singing a sad, sad, old, wounded animal!

line: Look, I’m just saying, if she wants to leave I‘m not gonna threaten her.

name: Agent
line: Look at her! Look at her. Look at how fickle this family is!

name: Rick
line: I’ve seen enough of this to know that when our son shows up in a couple of crucial situations, we can’d like, you know, end up getting him to the hospital and having him wrapped up in bubble wrap for the night and dropping it to the floor and dropping to the carpet!

name: Agent
line: The day the shit hits is all over her! All right, Morty, you made it real loud and loud!

name: Rick
line: That’ll take a lot of damage!
